Nakuru senator Susan Kihika on Saturday celebrated her traditional wedding to her groom Sam Mburu. Mburu who is a businessman, formalised his union to the Nakuru Senator in front of over 100 guests in Nyahururu area. DP William Ruto was among guests invited for the traditional ceremony . A number of Ruto's allies also attended the ceremony including his personal assistant Faruk Kibet, Kapseret MP Oscar Sudi, Malindi MP Aisha Jumwa among others. The groom and the bride have had a publicised relationship over the past years when they met on the campaign trail. Mburu, a close associate of Ruto, was campaigning for the Jubilee campaign team when he met Kihika .